      "content": "hey, im feeling kinda weird. my left arm feels super heavy and kinda tingly like it's asleep but it won't wake up. also my voice sounds a bit thick/slurred when i talk. i just got back from a long flight from tokyo... do u think i'm just exhausted or dehydrated?",
